products.body_html:
We got so much feedback that y’all wanted to swap the pita for a wrap so as always, we heard ya fam! We’re proud to introduce the the ultimate grab-and-go meal… Minted Lamb Tortilla + Spring Greens

Think tender, minted lamb stuffed with the freshest salad you have ever seen - including spinach, cherry toms, radish and cucumber. And for some extra zing, we’ve added in some refreshing minty Greek yogurt

products.title: Moroccan Chicken Tagine
products.body_html:
We’re taking your taste buds on a journey down the streets of Morocco with our new Moroccan Chicken Tagine. It’s a party in your mouth with a wonderful blend of aromatic tastes from Morocco.

This delicious, flavourful summer dish is jam packed with goodness for your body starting with the fresh side salad, filled with asparagus, spanish onion and cherry tomoatos mixed through a handful of brown rice. Then… wait for it fam… there is the juicy goodness of the chicken + tagine sauce! Slow cooked to perfection and blended with the best Moroccan spices, dried fruit and pistachios.

Topped with a bit of mouth cleansing tzatziki for a lil’ bit of flavour contrast. Oh… and don’t forget to soak up all those deliciously, juicy sauces with the naan bread!
